---
title: Springtime Chicken Casserole with Bacon, Crème Fraîche and Sliced Spring Greens
description: Chicken thighs are wonderfully forgiving. If you’re not quite ready for dinner, they can sit in the oven for a long time and remain flavourful and moist. This is a customisable casserole - mild for those who don't like things too hot but with a sweet-and-spicy chilli drizzle for those that want to zhush things up a bit.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-casserole-32456421-989e9b06.jpg
